metadata.name: 01/15 - Trookie
metadata.description:
TROOKIE

The planet earth is now ruled by an elite of corrupts who have manipulated the human mind to eliminate creativity.

Tired of the world he lives in, Trookie tried to escape and fate will take him to an unexpected place, to the boundaries of creativity.

_______________________________

Made by Trookers to celebrate the metaverse designed for Jupiter Blockchain.

Storytelling and AI generated art by i8art | Trooker
